askForSpatialIndexCreation

public com.iver.utiles.swing.threads.IMonitorableTask askForSpatialIndexCreation(com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.layers.FLyrVect layer)
Asks to the user for the creation of a spatial index for the specified layer. It will be of help for certain geoprocesses. FLyrVect default spatial index is MapServer quadtree, that hasnt the ability to do nearest neighbour searches. For those geoprocesses that needs it (NN searches) overwrite this method and use JSI RTree, or SIL RTree. It returns an IMonitorableTask, a task to build the spatial index in background.

Parameters:
layer -
Returns:
an ITask
